<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-11-0648 </DOCNO><TEXT>Most HPI companies have need for an easy to use planning tool to evaluatecogeneration opportunities without extensive study, to see quickly ifaddition or modification to their existing cogeneration facilities couldbe justified economically. This article provides such a planning tool,using a sound thermodynamic base and offering a good indication of incentivesto be found open further detailed study.</TEXT></DOC>